<TD WIDTH="67%">
<H4>
Welcome to my web pages!
</H4>
<p align="justify"> I am an academic in the School of Mathematical Sciences at Queen Mary, University of London, where I hold the position of Reader in Applied Mathematics. 
I am interested in lattice statistical mechanics, combinatorics, dynamical systems, Monte Carlo algorithms, and soft condensed matter.
I am affiliated with the Technical University Clausthal in Germany, where I hold the title of Professor. 
I am also an Associate Investigator of the Centre of Excellence for Mathematics and Statistics of Complex Systems at the University of Melbourne in Australia.
</p>
</TD>
